msgstr "``NEIGHBORS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1527
msgid "Default: 1"
msgstr "기본값: 1"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1528
msgid "Maximum number of neighbors to look for"
msgstr "검색할 이웃의 최대 개수"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1529
msgid "**Maximum distance**"
msgstr "**Maximum distance**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1532
msgid "``DISTANCE``"
msgstr "``DISTANCE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1534
msgid ""
"Only destination features which are closer than this distance will be "
"considered."
msgstr "이 거리보다 가까이 있는 대상 피처만 연산에 넣을 것입니다."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1536
msgid "**Shortest lines**"
msgstr "**Shortest lines**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1559
msgid "**Output layer**"
msgstr "**Output layer**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1562
msgid ""
"Line vector layer joining source features to their nearest neighbor(s) in "
"the destination layer. Contains all attributes for both source and "
"destination features, and the computed distance."
msgstr ""
"대상 레이어의 대응하는 최근접 이웃(들)에 소스 피처를 결합시킨 라인 벡터 레이어입니다. 소스 피처와 대상 피처의 모든 속성과 계산한 "
"거리를 담고 있습니다."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1569
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:shortestline``"
msgstr "**알고리즘 ID**: ``native:shortestline``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1579
msgid "ST-DBSCAN clustering"
msgstr "ST-DBSCAN 군집 형성"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1581
msgid ""
"Clusters point features based on a 2D implementation of spatiotemporal "
"Density-based clustering of applications with noise (ST-DBSCAN) algorithm."
msgstr ""
"이상값(noise) (ST-DBSCAN) 알고리즘을 가진 응용 프로그램의 시공간 밀도 기반 군집 형성의 2차원 구현을 기반으로 포인트 "
"피처를 군집시킵니다."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1584
msgid ":ref:`qgisdbscanclustering`, :ref:`qgiskmeansclustering`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisdbscanclustering`, :ref:`qgiskmeansclustering`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1605
msgid "**Date/time field**"
msgstr "**Date/time field**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1606
msgid "``DATETIME_FIELD``"
msgstr "``DATETIME_FIELD``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1607
msgid "[tablefield: date]"
msgstr "[tablefield: date]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1608
msgid "Field containing the temporal information"
msgstr "시계열 정보를 담고 있는 필드"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1622
msgid "**Maximum time duration between clustered points**"
msgstr "**Maximum time duration between clustered points**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1623
msgid "``EPS2``"
msgstr "``EPS2``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1626
msgid "Default: 0.0 (days)"
msgstr "기본값: 0.0 (days)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1627
msgid ""
"Time duration beyond which two features can not belong to the same cluster "
"(eps2). Available time units are milliseconds, seconds, minutes, hours, days"
" and weeks."
msgstr ""
"이 기간을 초과하면 피처 2개가 동일 군집(eps2)에 속할 수 없습니다. 밀리초, 초, 분, 시, 일 및 주(週) 단위를 사용할 수 "
"있습니다."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1702
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:stdbscanclustering``"
msgstr "**알고리즘 ID**: ``native:stdbscanclustering``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1712
msgid "Statistics by categories"
msgstr "범주 통계"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1713
msgid ""
"Calculates statistics of a field depending on a parent class. The parent "
